294
00:14:56,889 --> 00:14:57,723
-There's no need to--

295
00:14:57,823 --> 00:15:00,323
-Ranma says forget
the cute type.

296
00:15:00,423 --> 00:15:04,123
What you need is the brute
strength of an Akane.

297
00:15:04,223 --> 00:15:05,389
[boom]

298
00:15:05,489 --> 00:15:07,789
-One of these days I'll
remember why I put up with you.

299
00:15:07,889 --> 00:15:08,623
-[groans]

300
00:15:08,723 --> 00:15:10,089
-But until then it's goodbye!

