whole life for all I care.

307
00:15:29,456 --> 00:15:30,756
Geez!

308
00:15:30,856 --> 00:15:31,723
Why do I even--

309
00:15:34,689 --> 00:15:41,156
-It's that dumb Akane
always got to-- huh?

310
00:15:41,256 --> 00:15:42,523
Huh?

311
00:15:42,623 --> 00:15:43,064
What?

312
00:15:43,123 --> 00:15:43,564
He scores!

313
00:15:47,523 --> 00:15:50,089
Ugh, iron geta?

314
00:15:50,189 --> 00:15:52,589
Lead-weighted obi?

315
00:15:52,689 --> 00:15:55,023
Yukata woven with chains?

316
00:15:55,123 --> 00:15:55,564
-[scream]

