00:15:55,623 --> 00:15:56,489
-Huh?

318
00:15:56,589 --> 00:15:57,489
-Oh.

319
00:15:57,589 --> 00:15:58,956
Oh.

320
00:15:59,056 --> 00:16:03,123
--[straining sound]
Akane, what are you--

321
00:16:03,223 --> 00:16:04,489
-Ranma.

322
00:16:04,589 --> 00:16:05,523
-Hang on.

323
00:16:05,623 --> 00:16:06,956
I'll be right there.
[straining sound]

324
00:16:08,589 --> 00:16:09,756
-Oh, just leave me alone.

325
00:16:09,856 --> 00:16:11,689
I got scared, that's all.

326
00:16:11,789 --> 00:16:13,323
I don't need your help.

327
00:16:13,423 --> 00:16:16,456
I'm a brute, remember?

328
00:16:16,556 --> 00:16:19,189
-Akane, you're making a
big deal out of nothing.

329
00:16:19,289 --> 00:16:20,823
What's important
is I want your--

330
00:16:20,923 --> 00:16:21,405
-No.

331
00:16:21,423 --> 00:16:22,723
-Huh?

332
00:16:22,823 --> 00:16:25,656
-What's important is I invited
you because I-- oh, never mind.

333
00:16:25,756 --> 00:16:28,089
It's not me you want anyway.

334
00:16:28,189 --> 00:16:29,656
It's my brute strength.

335
00:16:29,756 --> 00:16:31,023
-Huh?

336
00:16:31,123 --> 00:16:33,256
I-- I don't remember any--

337
00:16:33,356 --> 00:16:36,123
-I said never mind.

338
00:16:36,223 --> 00:16:38,689
-Akane, Akane, wait.

339
00:16:38,789 --> 00:16:40,789
At least tell me why you're so--

340
00:16:40,889 --> 00:16:42,189
-I told you.

341
00:16:42,289 --> 00:16:43,623
Oh!

342
00:16:43,723 --> 00:16:45,023
Oh!

343
00:16:45,123 --> 00:16:50,089
ANNOUNCER: (LAUGHING) Welcome
to the bath of shifting sands.

344
00:16:50,189 --> 00:16:52,489
-You're standing too close.

345
00:16:52,589 --> 00:16:53,889
-No, I'm sinking too close.

346
00:16:53,989 --> 00:16:57,689
And if you hadn't made me follow
you, then we wouldn't be here.

347
00:16:57,789 --> 00:16:59,989
Hey, it stopped moving.

348
00:17:00,089 --> 00:17:00,530
-Oh.

349
00:17:03,156 --> 00:17:04,856
I really am sorry.

350
00:17:04,956 --> 00:17:06,023
You're right.

351
00:17:06,123 --> 00:17:06,589
It's my fault.

352
00:17:06,689 --> 00:17:08,456
-Huh?

353
00:17:08,556 --> 00:17:09,023
-Go on.

354
00:17:09,123 --> 00:17:10,456
Get out of here.

355
00:17:10,556 --> 00:17:11,156
-Ha!

356
00:17:11,256 --> 00:17:12,523
You're such a kidder.

357
00:17:12,623 --> 00:17:15,089
I almost thought you
were like-- serious.

358
00:17:15,189 --> 00:17:17,323
-I mean it, Ranma.

359
00:17:17,423 --> 00:17:19,289
Get out of my face
while you still can

360
00:17:19,389 --> 00:17:22,656
or I swear to you you're
going to regret you ever--

361
00:17:22,756 --> 00:17:23,589
-Oh!

362
00:17:23,689 --> 00:17:24,623
Hey, stupid.

363
00:17:24,723 --> 00:17:27,856
You still haven't
said what I did to--

364
00:17:27,956 --> 00:17:29,689
-I invited you because--

365
00:17:29,789 --> 00:17:30,689
-Uh, oh.

366
00:17:30,789 --> 00:17:32,189
AKANE (VOICEOVER):
You want to come?

367
00:17:32,289 --> 00:17:33,356
It's already paid for.

368
00:17:33,456 --> 00:17:35,123
And if we win this contest
we're holding, we--

369
00:17:37,956 --> 00:17:39,356
-Oh, please.

370
00:17:39,456 --> 00:17:41,689
This is not supposed
to be happening.

371
00:17:41,789 --> 00:17:45,089
All I ever wanted was for Ranma
to win that trip, you know?

372
00:17:45,189 --> 00:17:45,723
So we--

373
00:17:45,823 --> 00:17:46,589
-If that's true--

374
00:17:46,689 --> 00:17:47,889
-Huh?

375
00:17:47,989 --> 00:17:51,289
- --then why are you trying
so hard to make me angry?

376
00:17:51,389 --> 00:17:53,156
-Me make you angry?

377
00:17:53,256 --> 00:17:55,523
How dare you?

378
00:17:55,623 --> 00:17:56,956
-I'm sorry, OK.

379
00:17:57,056 --> 00:17:59,089
I didn't realize
you'd invited me.

380
00:17:59,189 --> 00:18:02,823
-You-- you came back
to say you were sorry?

381
00:18:02,923 --> 00:18:03,356
-Sorry.

382
00:18:03,456 --> 00:18:04,089
Yep.

383
00:18:04,189 --> 00:18:05,356
Uh-huh.

384
00:18:05,456 --> 00:18:08,356
And for what it's worth ,
I accept your apology too.

385
00:18:08,456 --> 00:18:10,989
-Gee, isn't that
generous of you?

386
00:18:11,089 --> 00:18:12,089
Huh?

387
00:18:12,189 --> 00:18:12,789
[boing]

388
00:18:13,589 --> 00:18:14,656
-Man this is easy.

389
00:18:14,756 --> 00:18:15,823
-Oh, oh, great.

390
00:18:15,923 --> 00:18:16,989
They're ahead.

391
00:18:17,089 --> 00:18:18,756
Look, there's no time to fight.

392
00:18:18,856 --> 00:18:20,989
Just trust me, OK?

393
00:18:21,089 --> 00:18:22,389
-What?

394
00:18:22,489 --> 00:18:23,489
Oh, what are you doing?

395
00:18:23,589 --> 00:18:25,656
-What's it look like I'm doing?

396
00:18:25,756 --> 00:18:27,623
First, I'm going to throw you.

397
00:18:27,723 --> 00:18:32,056
Then I'm uh, then I'm, um, oh--

398
00:18:32,156 --> 00:18:33,056
-Ranma!

399
00:18:33,156 --> 00:18:35,656
Oh!

400
00:18:35,756 --> 00:18:36,989
-[coughing]

401
00:18:37,089 --> 00:18:37,923
-What is it?

402
00:18:38,023 --> 00:18:39,123
What's wrong?

403
00:18:39,223 --> 00:18:40,656
-The rope's too heavy.

404
00:18:40,756 --> 00:18:43,656
-But-- oh, I get it.

405
00:18:43,756 --> 00:18:44,197
Here I'll--

406
00:18:44,256 --> 00:18:45,156
-Oh--

407
00:18:45,256 --> 00:18:45,697
-See this?

408
00:18:45,756 --> 00:18:47,123
-Wait!

409
00:18:47,223 --> 00:18:49,089
-Here it goes!

410
00:18:49,189 --> 00:18:49,630
Ah!

411
00:18:58,589 --> 00:19:03,056
[straining] Oh, there,
that ought to hold.

412
00:19:03,156 --> 00:19:05,823
-You're, uh, kind of
good at this stuff.

413
00:19:13,156 --> 00:19:14,223
[music playing]

414
00:19:15,989 --> 00:19:16,856
-Oh!

415
00:19:16,956 --> 00:19:20,189
-Oh, no, They're
heading this way.

416
00:19:20,289 --> 00:19:20,889
[panting]

417
00:19:22,289 --> 00:19:25,223
-Unless something happens,
they're going to win, Akane.

418
00:19:25,323 --> 00:19:28,323
[panting]

419
00:19:28,423 --> 00:19:30,956
-Let a couple of
punks like that win

420
00:19:31,056 --> 00:19:33,356
after what we've been through?

421
00:19:33,456 --> 00:19:35,856
We ain't beat yet, are we boys?

422
00:19:35,956 --> 00:19:37,356
-No, sir!

423
00:19:37,456 --> 00:19:38,856
-Yes!

424
00:19:38,956 --> 00:19:39,856
-Oh, it's running away.

425
00:19:43,456 --> 00:19:44,256
-Faster men.

426
00:19:44,356 --> 00:19:45,256
Run faster!

427
00:19:45,356 --> 00:19:46,723
-They're insane.

428
00:19:46,823 --> 00:19:49,156
-Move it, Mousse.

429
00:19:49,256 --> 00:19:51,123
-Let's do it.

430
00:19:51,223 --> 00:19:53,089
[music playing]

431
00:19:56,123 --> 00:19:57,956
-Hey, you guys!

432
00:19:58,056 --> 00:19:58,497
-Wake up!

433
00:19:58,556 --> 00:20:00,923
Oh!

434
00:20:01,023 --> 00:20:01,923
-This is it.

435
00:20:02,023 --> 00:20:05,356
We're almost there.

436
00:20:05,456 --> 00:20:06,356
-Ranma, I'm so happy.

437
00:20:16,356 --> 00:20:18,123
-Akane, thank you.

438
00:20:18,223 --> 00:20:20,356
I owe you big time.

439
00:20:20,456 --> 00:20:22,156
-Sure.

440
00:20:22,256 --> 00:20:26,389
-Ready or not,
Jusenkyo here we come.

441
00:20:26,489 --> 00:20:27,456
[straining sounds]

442
00:20:28,889 --> 00:20:31,523
-I told you we shouldn't
have come this way.

443
00:20:31,623 --> 00:20:32,356
-What?

444
00:20:32,456 --> 00:20:33,323
-Huh?

445
00:20:33,423 --> 00:20:35,789
[music playing]

446
00:20:45,223 --> 00:20:45,705
-What?

447
00:20:45,723 --> 00:20:46,164
What?

448
00:20:54,689 --> 00:20:56,589
-We were almost there.

449
00:20:56,689 --> 00:20:59,456
-Yeah, thanks for
nothing, Ryoga.

450
00:20:59,556 --> 00:21:04,623
--[laughter] Hey,
tough luck, Saotome.

451
00:21:04,723 --> 00:21:08,223
And I'll see you when
I get back, Akane.

452
00:21:08,323 --> 00:21:11,423
-He must have really
have wanted to go.

